# Defensive: this project's real credentials/tokens never belong inside the
# repo (login persists to ~/.precomcli/config.json, outside the working
# directory, by design - see CLAUDE.md). These patterns are a backstop
# against ever accidentally adding a stray secrets file here.
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*credentials*
*secrets*
